842
00:35:13,490 --> 00:35:13,970
Ms. Lan,

843
00:35:14,530 --> 00:35:15,610
you're eager to go abroad.

844
00:35:16,170 --> 00:35:17,530
I'd like to know

845
00:35:17,530 --> 00:35:18,970
