846
00:35:25,490 --> 00:35:26,450
I won't let anyone

847
00:35:26,450 --> 00:35:27,370
take the blame for me.

848
00:35:27,890 --> 00:35:28,730
Bro.

849
00:35:31,130 --> 00:35:32,010
You have to take the fall

850
00:35:32,010 --> 00:35:33,250
