853
00:35:36,730 --> 00:35:37,610
against Luowei Yulan.

854
00:35:39,370 --> 00:35:39,970
Aunt.

855
00:35:41,050 --> 00:35:42,810
You won't be able to take this flight.

856
00:35:43,410 --> 00:35:44,690
